text: Tau Ceti e, also called 52 Ceti e, is a possibly real exoplanet orbiting (going around) Tau Ceti. It was detected in 2012 by using tools and their data to analyze if it is a planet. It would orbit between Venus and Mercury at a distance of 0.552 AU with an orbital period of 168 days. It has a minimum mass of 3.93 Earth masses. ==References== Category:Exoplanets
title: Tau Ceti e
